3 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-12-02:the-hong-kong-i-love-zh.html</guid><category>Snippets</category><category>Snippets</category></item><item><title>读后感：《稀缺》</title><link>scarcity-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;As our island of knowledge grows, so does the shore of our ignorance.&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-10-09:scarcity-zh.html</guid><category>Snippets</category><category>Snippets</category></item><item><title>读后感：《苏世民：我的经验与教训》《助推》</title><link>what-it-takes-and-nudge-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;《苏世民：我的经验与教训》和《助推》读后感。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-09-12:what-it-takes-and-nudge-zh.html</guid><category>Snippets</category><category>Snippets</category></item><item><title>从股东财富最大化到利益相关方影响最大化</title><link>from-maximizing-shareholder-value-to-maximizing-stakeholder-impact-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从股东财富最大化（maximize shareholder value）到利益相关方影响最大化（maximize stakeholder impact）：我们需要从头定义企业存在的基础，不只是为了短期和长期的经济利益，而是以一种“命运共同体”的理念，以利益相关方影响最大化（maximize stakeholder impact）为核心，重新设计、调整、协调商业与市场模式。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 21 May 2023 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-05-21:from-maximizing-shareholder-value-to-maximizing-stakeholder-impact-zh.html</guid><category>Snippets</category><category>Snippets</category></item><item><title>写在读书日</title><link>on-world-book-day-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;书是生活的影子，是一面镜子。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 23 Apr 2023 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-04-23:on-world-book-day-zh.html</guid><category>Snippets</category><category>Snippets</category></item><item><title>对立平衡与动态稳定 Contrapposto and Dynamic Stability-苏博西馆“古希腊人：运动员、战士与英雄“观后感</title><link>contrapposto-and-dynamic-stability-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;古希腊是一个日常生活、文体宗教都高度繁荣的时期。在繁荣稳定的背后是存在于不同场景中的对抗与竞争。这种动态的对抗力为稳定提供了支持，是一种“动态稳定”。展品中的雕像、陶罐纹样都有一种静止的动感、一种不对称的平衡感。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 04 Apr 2023 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-04-04:contrapposto-and-dynamic-stability-zh.html</guid><category>Art</category><category>Art</category></item><item><title>拙政园游记</title><link>the-humble-administrator-s-garden-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;游玩园林最好的方式就是把它当成自家院子&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Mar 2023 21:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2023-03-29:the-humble-administrator-s-garden-zh.html</guid><category>Art</category><category>Art</category></item><item><title>白天谈吃｜Bouley &amp; 料理人上田</title><link>Bouley-UEDA-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;太emo了，想想吃的吧。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 13 Mar 2022 14:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2022-03-13:Bouley-UEDA-zh.html</guid><category>Food</category><category>Food</category></item><item><title>My Green World - The MET</title><link>my-green-world-zh.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;大都会，永远的绿色世界。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Iris</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 10 Mar 2022 21:56:00 +0800</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:None,2022-03-10:my-green-world-zh.html</guid><category>Art</category><category>Art</category></item></channel></rss>